{"tid":2037340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"奶共Google 話刪批評中共嘅comment 係系統錯誤喎","createTime":"2020-05-27T02:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T03:06:23.000Z","uid":198088,"like":17,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"87fe14519a0bb277fa72bb242f80ce3ecc705746","tid":2037340,"uid":198088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:30:51.000Z","msg":"根據The Verge 報導，Google 旗下嘅YouTube 會自動刪除含有「五毛」、「共匪」字眼嘅comment。而家The Verge 上門追問，Google 就賴係AI出錯。佢話喎，係因為疫情，令到人分配有變，依賴多左AI filter，所以唔知點解要加左呢啲keyword 入個filter，而家就查緊點解。<br />\n<br />\nThe Verge 就踢爆早到上年十月YouTube 已經刪緊comment, 仲屌Google 個Dragonfly 計劃，同埋數佢奶共咁話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2020/5/26/21270290/youtube-deleting-comments-censorship-chinese-communist-party-ccp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2020%2F5%2F26%2F21270290%2Fyoutube-deleting-comments-censorship-chinese-communist-party-ccp&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8UzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=9308bed2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2020/5/26/21270290/youtube-deleting-comments-censorship-chinese-communist-party-ccp</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogle 食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40659af1146a34642c58e87157f250a02e74c884","tid":2037340,"uid":198088,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:32:12.000Z","msg":"如果可以，少用Google 嘢，因為你嘅私隱俾Google 當錢使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5baf39a6d65919917331b96f4fc4e35cf820447","tid":2037340,"uid":2772,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:33:32.000Z","msg":"遲D AI真係識諗野<br />\n隨時殺撚哂GOOGLE D人<br />\n成撚日屈鳩佢錯"},{"pid":"86f7750f5c78f35f4e7c0fe5f4305185c85355a6","tid":2037340,"uid":147916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:34:31.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗奶到咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i